&lt;p&gt;Timescale powers the next wave of computing, and we are enabling our customers to build innovative, data-centric applications powered by Timescale. As a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Account Executive - Commercial, &lt;/strong&gt;you will interact directly with customers, answer questions, provide information, and build connections with them.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will be at the forefront of closing deals and providing solutions in our growing database market. You can make a meaningful impact by helping organizations harness the power of data for better decision-making, improved operations, and innovation. You will manage complex sales relationships with critical customers and effectively communicate the value of Timescale. As the company and industry expand, we see our high-growth market as an opportunity for significant sales and career advancement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your main responsibilities will include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Focus on closing Sales Qualified Leads (SQL) from the marketing team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Providing mentorship to AEs and BDRs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Qualify leads based on their challenges and alignment with our product suite.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategically prospect into CTOs, Engineering Leads, and Technical End Users.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the full sales cycle.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage resources such as Sales Engineers and Data Architects effectively.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide relevant stakeholders through the sales process to close.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A little bit about you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are a top performer with a proven track record, and you know that your success directly depends on your customers&#39; success. You always put the customer&#39;s best interests first while managing complex sales engagements and effectively leveraging resources to ensure success. You are hungry, resilient, curious, driven, and humble in your pursuit of excellence. You arenâ€™t afraid to speak up and identify problem areas or share your ideas, and you want to be a &lt;strong&gt;part of the solution&lt;/strong&gt;! You are a builder who is passionate about creatively trying new things and contributing to our growth by exploring innovative solutions ðŸ™Œ.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You also have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;3+ years of experience in a full-cycle quota-carrying Saas sales role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Technical background with a deep understanding of database technology, data platforms, open source, and cloud ecosystems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Ability to articulate the business value of complex enterprise technology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Proficiency in modern sales software (e.g., Salesforce, Outreach, etc.).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Proven track record of exceeding sales targets and driving revenue growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Strong interpersonal skills with the ability to build rapport and establish trust with customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Demonstrated ability to manage multiple priorities in a fast-paced environment effectively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Entrepreneurial mindset with a proactive approach to problem-solving.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
